Hi @mfichman, Have we intentionally removed `pdf_client` from `clients_factory` as part of this PR or just a auto-refactoring issue:- https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/74427?
If yes, then we need to a cleanup to remove the usage `pdf_client` from our codebase accordingly. Currenlty, CIs are failing due to mypy issues thrown for `pdf_client`.
